1997;;Best Men;;American;;Tamra Davis;;Fred Ward, Drew Barrymore;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Best_Men;;Jesse Reilly was released from prison and he is to be married to Hope. Shortly before the wedding, he is involved in a bank robbery with his friends Buzz Thomas, Teddy Pollack and Billy Phillips. It escalates to a hostage crisis, and the FBI is called. In an exchange of fire, a few men are shot. Hope and Jesse are then rescued by John G. Coleman in a helicopter.<br><br>In the final scene, Jesse and Hope raise their son.